{"tid":1436942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【再合理地爭取民意支持】","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:22:24.000Z","uid":87915,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"de6c22e17c1c62979388ec8ad1178497b1918c8e","tid":1436942,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"其實只要大家設定時限<br />\n我建議兩個禮拜，比政府做出回應行動<br />\n因為政府話要停止暴力先講，就停兩個禮拜<br />\n(利申：大家應該同我預期一樣，應該係無回應）<br />\n<br />\n亦講到明，兩星期後，後果自負<br />\n<br />\n期間，遊行集會，想做就做，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但要散</span><br />\n以兩星期時間蘊釀第二次大罷工，罷工日期置於限期後<br />\n<br />\n目的係<br />\n1. 我地要比市民睇  我地係班有理性嘅人<br />\n2. 義士休息<br />\n3. 拋個波比政府  (唔係重點）<br />\n4. 市民自然期望政府出招<br />\n5. 合理地政府唔會做嘢<br />\n6. 兩星期限期到，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">If we burn, you burn with us</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同意請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 再推post<br />\n不同意請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 不推post 回覆討論"},{"pid":"e417718c42dea25e11a99be98a8236acee2ba8b7","tid":1436942,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3601969facd1a6536b1c04a80dc074a0f4e9e95f","tid":1436942,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b79d9156588c467ff383af5d229d3d8044931ca5","tid":1436942,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79412e1d1194f02393e0e5429b7d1e190cc721e3","tid":1436942,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e2a8d0b0f0ff2c1abfd43f817608d0a432ae91a","tid":1436942,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:46:15.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"10918fbfdc594691f0572ab2af3c835b0f2bf96b","tid":1436942,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,